Package: promethiumR
Title: Advanced Seismic Data Recovery and Reconstruction Framework
Version: 1.0.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Olaf Yunus", "Laitinen Imanov", , "contact@promethium.dev", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Native R implementation of the Promethium seismic data recovery 
    framework. Provides algorithms for denoising, interpolation, matrix 
    completion, and deep learning-based reconstruction of seismic data.
    Implements the shared Promethium specification for cross-language consistency.
